<br>
Relik was the epitome of a Chaotic/Neutral personna.  A badguy looking out only for himself who sometimes would reveal a heart of gold.  <br>
<br>
RIP Ernie, Nick and Relik. <br>
<br>
My favorite modern CBC shows are North of 60, Street Legal and Street Cents.  Steet Cents is brilliant, helping to reveal to our youth that they are often targets of big business and corporate/consumer agenda.   Fit for the Pit!!<br>
<br>
Anyway I don't where I was going with the above except perhaps to say I'm proud of the quality of television produced in this country.  From sea to sea to sea, WE are the CBC.  =)<br>
<br>
Signing for another programming day..<br>
